{"id":477968,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":23}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"毛主席是我们心中的最红最红的太阳　毛泽东思想是我们革命的最亮最亮的灯塔","genre":"","count":"213","ytitle":"","mtitle":"红卫兵之歌","ftitle":"","authors":["郑成义"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑成义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红袖章，红潮滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色尖兵在前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是统帅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是他的小兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打头阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢干敢闯敢革命!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫伟大的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁打江山万年春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤卫队——红卫兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过革命的枪杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父辈们英雄血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们心上腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫除一切害人虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大破四旧，大立四新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫伟大的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁打江山万年春。"}]}